Package: NetCoupler
Title: Inference of Causal Links Between a Network and an External Variable
Version: 0.0.4.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Luke",
             family = "Johnston",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "lwjohnst@gmail.com"),
      person(given = "Clemens",
